net.proteusframework.internet.dataprovider

Interface DataProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaScriptInitProvider, LinkDataProvider, MetaInformationProvider, NamespaceProvider

    public interface DataProvider
    Provides data to web page generation code. Data must be provided before rendering. The provided data is available at the time of rendering to components that can use it.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      String getIdentityOfData()
      Get a string that uniquely identifies the data provided.

      • getIdentityOfData

      • getIdentityOfDataConsumer

        DataIdentityConsumer getIdentityOfDataConsumer()
        Returns the responsible party for the identity of the data.
